{"data":{"properties":{"created_at":1631318877000,"events":{},"identifier":"layouts/group","modified_at":1631318877000,"properties":{"Group":[{"name":"orientation","description":"<p>Sets the <code>Group</code> to render its children vertically.</p>\n","types":["vertical"]},{"name":"variation","description":"<p>Sets how the <code>Group</code> should display the its children relative to the previous item.</p>\n","types":["stacked"]}]},"sections":[{"identifier":"group","level":1,"text":"Group"},{"identifier":"imports","level":2,"text":"Imports"},{"identifier":"orientation","level":2,"text":"Orientation"},{"identifier":"stacked","level":2,"text":"Stacked"}],"snippets":[{"identifier":"group-preview","script":"<script>\n    import {Button, Group} from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>\n\n<Group>\n    <Button>Button 1</Button>\n    <Button>Button 2</Button>\n    <Button>Button 3</Button>\n</Group>","syntax":"svelte","title":"Group Preview"},{"identifier":"group-imports","script":"<script>\n    import {Group} from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>","syntax":"html","title":"Group Imports"},{"identifier":"group-orientation","script":"<script>\n    import {\n        Button,\n        Box,\n        Group,\n        Stack,\n        Text,\n    } from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>\n\n<Stack\n    orientation=\"horizontal\"\n    spacing=\"medium\"\n    variation=\"wrap\"\n>\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">DEFAULT</Text>\n        <Box palette=\"dark\" padding=\"small\">\n            <Group>\n                <Button>Button 1</Button>\n                <Button>Button 2</Button>\n                <Button>Button 3</Button>\n            </Group>\n        </Box>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">VERTICAL</Text>\n        <Box palette=\"dark\" padding=\"small\">\n            <Group orientation=\"vertical\">\n                <Button>Button 1</Button>\n                <Button>Button 2</Button>\n                <Button>Button 3</Button>\n            </Group>\n        </Box>\n    </div>\n</Stack>","syntax":"svelte","title":"Group Orientation"},{"identifier":"group-stacked","script":"<script>\n    import {\n        Figure,\n        Group,\n        Stack,\n        Text,\n    } from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>\n\n<Stack\n    class=\"group-stacked\"\n    orientation=\"horizontal\"\n    spacing=\"medium\"\n    variation=\"wrap\"\n>\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">DEFAULT</Text>\n        <Group variation=\"stacked\">\n            <Figure\n                variation=\"icon\"\n                size=\"medium\"\n                shape=\"pill\"\n            >\n                <img src={IMAGE_AVATAR} />\n            </Figure>\n\n            <Figure\n                variation=\"icon\"\n                size=\"medium\"\n                shape=\"pill\"\n            >\n                <img src={IMAGE_AVATAR} />\n            </Figure>\n\n            <Figure\n                variation=\"icon\"\n                size=\"medium\"\n                shape=\"pill\"\n            >\n                <img src={IMAGE_AVATAR} />\n            </Figure>\n\n            <Stack\n                alignment_y=\"center\"\n                padding_left=\"small\"\n            >\n                <Text is=\"small\">+7</Text>\n            </Stack>\n        </Group>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">VERTICAL</Text>\n        <Group\n            variation=\"stacked\"\n            orientation=\"vertical\"\n        >\n            <Figure\n                variation=\"icon\"\n                size=\"medium\"\n                shape=\"pill\"\n            >\n                <img src={IMAGE_AVATAR} />\n            </Figure>\n\n            <Figure\n                variation=\"icon\"\n                size=\"medium\"\n                shape=\"pill\"\n            >\n                <img src={IMAGE_AVATAR} />\n            </Figure>\n\n            <Figure\n                variation=\"icon\"\n                size=\"medium\"\n                shape=\"pill\"\n            >\n                <img src={IMAGE_AVATAR} />\n            </Figure>\n\n            <Stack\n                alignment_x=\"center\"\n                padding_top=\"small\"\n            >\n                <Text is=\"small\">+7</Text>\n            </Stack>\n        </Group>\n    </div>\n</Stack>\n\n<style>\n    :global(.group-stacked strong) {\n        display: block;\n    }\n</style>","syntax":"svelte","title":"Group Stacked"}],"title":"Group"},"render":"<h1 id=\"group\">Group</h1>\n<p><code>Group</code> is a layout primitive used for grouping together like Components with their inner border radii removed.</p>\n<iframe\n    class=\"snippet-repl\"\n    src=\"/repl/docs/layouts/group/group-preview?rotation=horizontal\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-top-navigation allow-modals allow-same-origin\" loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n<a href=\"/repl/docs/layouts/group/group-preview?rotation=horizontal\" hidden sveltekit:prefetch></a><h2 id=\"imports\">Imports</h2>\n<pre class=\"language-html snippet-highlight\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>Group<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@kahi-ui/framework\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre><h2 id=\"orientation\">Orientation</h2>\n<p>You can set the <code>Group</code> to render its children Components vertically, via the <code>orientation</code> property.</p>\n<iframe\n    class=\"snippet-repl\"\n    src=\"/repl/docs/layouts/group/group-orientation?rotation=horizontal\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-top-navigation allow-modals allow-same-origin\" loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n<a href=\"/repl/docs/layouts/group/group-orientation?rotation=horizontal\" hidden sveltekit:prefetch></a><h2 id=\"stacked\">Stacked</h2>\n<p>You can set the <code>variation</code> property to <code>stacked</code> to visually stack children Components, like avatar stacks.</p>\n<!--\n    TODO: Two more avatars, would probably look nicer without ones that would blend into each other\n-->\n<iframe\n    class=\"snippet-repl\"\n    src=\"/repl/docs/layouts/group/group-stacked?rotation=horizontal\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-top-navigation allow-modals allow-same-origin\" loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n<a href=\"/repl/docs/layouts/group/group-stacked?rotation=horizontal\" hidden sveltekit:prefetch></a>"}}